title: 820-00923 No POST
message: Hello. Got this one here with no post. VCORE stuck at 1.08V. Tried flashing BIOS, same results. Verified all termination resistors, everything OK. CPU gets warm. Tried heat and flux around CPU to see if there was any crap under it, still no good. Any ideas?

title: 820-00923 No POST
message:
Probably bad CPU.

PLT_RESET_L comes high?
Did you test the board alone on the desk?
